high_descs: Turn around, turn right, look at the cabinet.
Open the cabinet, take the toilet paper from the sink, close the cabinet.
Turn around, move right toward the cabinet.
Open the cabinet, put the toilet paper inside, close the cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Take the toilet paper from the sink, put it inside the cabinet.

high_descs: Turn around then turn right to the cabinet.
Take the toiletpaper roll from the sink.
Turn right then turn around to the cabinet top.
Place the toiletpaper roll in the cabinet under the counter top.
anns.task_desc: Take the ToiletPaper roll from the sink and Place the ToiletPaper roll in Cabinet under the counter top

high_descs: Exit from the cabinet, turn right, go straight, turn left, near to the sink.
Pick up the toiletpaper roll holder on the sink.
Turn around turn right to turn left near to cabinet
Keep the toiletpaper roll holder on the cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Keep the ToiletPaper roll holder on the Cabinet.
